snippet.title: StalakMiner - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1517870/StalakMiner

StalakMiner is a third-person action adventure digging game that presents strategical and timed mining challenges to you as a miner tasked with reaching the depths of the planet. Collect rare metals and minerals to sell for credits used to upgrade your vehicle.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1517870/StalakMiner/
